  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Rinse the <strong>brown rice</strong>, add it to a pot with plenty of <span class=\"text-highlight\"><strong>cold water</strong></span> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p>\r\n<p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to medium and cook for 20-25 min or until it's tender with a slight bite</p>\r\n<p>Once cooked, drain and run under cold water until cool</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1609.-step-1-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1609.-step-1-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1609.-step-1-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1609.-step-1-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1609.-step-1-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, trim and roughly chop the<strong> spring onions&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p>Peel and roughly chop the <strong>garlic</strong></p>\r\n<p>Peel (scrape the skin off with a teaspoon) and&nbsp;roughly&nbsp;chop (or grate) the <strong>ginger</strong></p>\r\n<p>Chop the <strong>smoked basa fillets</strong> into rough pieces</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1609.-step-2-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1609.-step-2-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1609.-step-2-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1609.-step-2-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1609.-step-2-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>chopped basa</strong>,<strong> ginger</strong>,<strong> garlic</strong>,<strong> spring onion</strong> and <strong>panko breadcrumbs</strong> to a <strong>food processor</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p>\r\n<p>Blitz until smooth <span class=\"text-highlight\">(Don</span>'t worry&nbsp;if it's a bit chunky)</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
